Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但婚姻辅导这事能随便说吗?\NYeah, but couples therapy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\NI don't know. Couples therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?咱两?婚姻辅导...这真是...\NRight? Us? Couples therapy... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太疯狂了\NThat's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 你做了什么?\NWoman, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,准确的说我们没去\NTechnically we did not go,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但在阿历克斯和戴夫分手后 我只是\Nbut after Alex and Dave split up, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我吓坏了 我想去见婚姻辅导师\NI was so freaked out, I wanted to go see a couples therapist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,确保我们很好 所以我想我会见一些\Nto make sure we were okay, so I thought I'd meet a few,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 看谁适合\Nyou know, see who fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你试了治疗师了?多少个?\NWait. You auditioned therapists? How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-五个-五个?\N- Five. - Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是五个!瞧 我本认为我们有交流障碍\NFive! See, I thought maybe we had trouble communicating,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但第一个治疗师说我们只是交流方式不同\Nbut the first doctor said we just had different styles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后接着 第二个治疗师说 我需要\Nand then, well, the second one said that, you know, I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,马上提出问题 而且他有口臭\Nto bring up issues sooner, and he had bad breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,接着第三个治疗师\Nand then third one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像个女版斯科特 巴古拉\Nlooked like a female Scott bakula,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我压力太大\Nwhich just stressed me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我"人到中年"还落后好多没看\Nbecause I am way behind on my "men of a certain age"s,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你知道妈妈多么喜欢一个干净的录像机\Nand you know how mama likes a clean dvr,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,接着第四个治疗师问我为什么\Nand then the fourth one asked me why
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,去找了这么多治疗师...\NI went to so many therapists...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不喜欢他...\NDid not like him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,接着第五个治疗师让我意识到\NAnd then the fifth one made me realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个很棒的老公和一段美好的婚姻\NI have an amazing husband and a great marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以周围一切都很好\Nso all is good in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-好 很好-我明白 你很生气\N- Good. Great. - Okay, you're mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你能敞开心扉\Nbut I wouldn't have had to go to all these therapists
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也用不着非得去找这些治疗师\Nif I thought that you would be open to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那么这是我的错了?行 随便你\NOh, so now it's on me? Okay. All right. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你要去哪儿?\NWell, wait. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去工作 因为我老婆发疯\NTo work, because my wife is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我没发疯 行吗?\NI am not insane, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 三 五治疗师确定我没疯\NDoctors one, three, and five confirmed that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在看什么? 为什么你带着\NWhat are we watching, and why are you carrying around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一只泰迪熊?\Na Teddy bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心莫里熊 他跟着我呢\NDon't worry about Murray the bear. He's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,另外阿历克斯跟我说了你梦游的事 我愿意\NAnd Alex told me about your sleepwalking. I am willing to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,打赌这个录像能证明你偷了该死的食物\Nbet that this tape proves that you stole the freakin' food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-她跟你说那个了?-哦 当然\N- She told you about that? - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 我没梦游!\NDude, I do not sleepwalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么每个人...啊!\NI don't know why everybody... aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-我梦游-嘣!抓到你了\N- I sleepwalk. - Boom! Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧吧 你正要去冰箱那儿\NSee, you're gonna go to the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,回头你有要去...然后你从冰箱走开\NSoon you're gonna go... and you're walking away from the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-那么谁偷的食物?-我为什么要鞠躬?\N- Well, who stole the food then? - And why was I bowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等!停!看见那个了吗?\NWait, wait, wait! Stop! Stop! Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?倒回去!\NHuh? Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-倒回去!-我在倒着呢!\N- Go back! - I am. I am going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 有人住在我们的天花板上吗?\NDude, is there a guy living in our ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 伙计 有个人住在我们的天花板上\NYes, dude. There's a guy living in our ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们要从马克斯那给你的商店弄油漆?\NWhy are we getting paint for your store from Max's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他有个朋友\NHe said he had a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,马克斯的银行账户是他床下的一个垃圾袋\NMax's bank account is a garbage bag under his bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但说到他有个涂油漆的朋友\Nbut he's got a paint guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,完全说得通\NMakes total sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 嘿\NOh. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 我叫马尔科姆\NHi. I'm Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 呃 戴夫和马克斯楼上的新邻居\NI'm, uh, Dave and Max's new upstairs neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们 呃...我没冰箱\NThey, um... I don't have a fridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们说我可以来这儿用他们的\Nso they said I could come in here and use theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我叫阿历克斯 她叫彭妮\NWell, I'm Alex, and this is penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们事实上只是来拿些油漆\NWe actually just came to pick up some paint,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显不在这儿\Nwhich is clearly not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 有趣 因为我事实上是名画家\NOh, that's funny, 'cause I'm actually a painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像拉斐尔或米开朗琪罗那样的?\NLike Raphael or Michelangelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 他们是文艺复兴时的\NWell, they were, like, renaissance guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我更像个概念艺术家-像多纳泰罗那样的?\N- I'm more of a conceptual artist. - Like donatello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上他是一名雕刻家\NWell, he was a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我只知道三个忍者神龟 我还是出局吧\NWell, I only know three ninja turtles, so I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是你最喜欢的?\NWho was your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,恩...艺术上讲 多纳泰罗\NUm... for art, donatello,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,论忍者神龟的话 就喜欢拉斐尔了\Nand for ninja turtling, Raphael all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,完全赞同\NTotally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿历克斯能跟你谈一小下吗? - 行?\N- Al? Can I talk to you for a skootch? - Yeah? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 看什么发生了\N- What? - See what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你放开自己去再次约会了\Nwhen you open yourself up to dating again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看机会来了! - 他?真的吗?\N- Look what comes along! - Him? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 他很可爱\NYeah. He is cute in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,像一个飞靶射击的乌尔里奇那样\Nlike, a Skeet Ulrich kinda way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他聪明 懂艺术 约他出去\NHe's smart. He's artistic. Ask him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 他是飞靶射击式的可爱\NOkay, he is skeet-cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道该不该\Nbut I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他是戴夫的邻居...\NHe's Dave's neighbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,特蕾西 鲁巴尔斯基（Dave睡了的那个高中放荡女）\NTracy lubarsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么马尔科姆 我不确定\NSo, Malcolm, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚想跟我喝一杯吗?\Nwould you like to maybe get a drink tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以深入讨论忍者神龟\NWe can dive into the whole ninja turtling debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来不了 - 哦\N- I can't. - Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去今晚的画廊开幕式\NUh, I've got the gallery opening tonight I'm supposed to be at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你想跟我一起去吗?\NUh, would you, I don't know, like to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 当然 我喜爱画廊开幕式!\NUh, yeah. I love gallery openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,酷 你去过很多吗?\NCool. Have you been to many?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 像有五 六千\N<i>Pfft. Uh... pfft, like, five, six... thousand.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她该在哪跟你碰面?\NWhere should she meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那就七点半在上西的画廊见吧\NUm, say, 7:30 at the gallery on west superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来真不错 说够了\NThat sounds super... erior. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜! - 我说了什么?抱歉啦!\N- Bye! - What was that? Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我约会了\NI'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐 我真为你感到骄傲 他看起来真棒\NOh, my God. I am so proud of you. He seems so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能找到一个正常的好男人，牺牲什么我都愿意啊\NOhh! What I wouldn't give to find a nice, normal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个偷食物的贼马上下来! 你知道\NYou get down here right now you food thief! You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,租我这地方的俄罗斯人告诉我这上面\Nthe Russian guy that rented me this place told me there was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个能爬行的空间 但我从没费工夫看过\Na crawl space up there, but I never even bothered to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你怕蜘蛛 老兄\NThat's 'cause you're afraid of spiders, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我第三大恐惧症\NIt's my third biggest phobia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,排在公众演讲和没化妆的变装皇后\Nbehind public speaking and drag queens with no makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们上去吧\NLet's go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定 老兄 这可相当高\NI don't know, man. It's pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 是个男人就上来\NCome on! Let's be men and get up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在容易 老兄\NIt's really easy, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在... 喔 天呐\NIt's really... Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这很难 这很难 这很难\NOkay. It's hard. It's hard. It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我上去了 快来吧!快来快来\NI got it. I got it. Come on now! Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄\NDude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在走廊发现另一个入口\NI found another entrance in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿有楼梯 走那儿比较容易\NIt had stairs. Way easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这地方没我想象的那样恐怖\NWow. This place is not as creepy as I thought it was gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把他的擦脸油都挤到他的篮子里\NI totally thought I was gonna be putting the lotion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但这家伙衬衫的品味还真不错\Nin the basket, but this guy's got pretty good taste in shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他其实是个很棒的艺术家\NHe's actually a pretty good artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全能从画中人的表情就感受到他们的痛苦\NYou can totally see the pain on this guy's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 老天\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿了我们的苹果脆片 他不能再拿了\NHe took our apple smacks! This has gotta stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要呆在这直到这大混蛋...\NWe are staying here until this bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 天呐\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过的最大的蜘蛛\NThat is the biggest spider I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我的错 这只是一个电线球\NOh. My bad. It's just a ball of wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫?\NDave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫?\NDave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿! 波拉德!怎么了 伙计?\NHey! "B"-rad! What's wrong, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那个会上太安静了\NYou were so quiet in that meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\NI mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你连在彼得森以他经典的o.J. 形象\Nyou didn't even laugh when Peterson whipped out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,冲出去的时候都没笑\Nhis classic o.J. Impression.
